{"tid":2054664,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葉劉淑儀稱將來審理「港區國安法」案件不宜安排陪審員","createTime":"2020-06-07T10:35:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T11:16:30.000Z","uid":291865,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5800c26ba47e850035027646461a37d6916978f1","tid":2054664,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T10:35:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/dZuFaHXHNUWagpYDx_EmbA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-06/de696720-a86e-11ea-ae67-9fe53df1bf3a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FdZuFaHXHNUWagpYDx_EmbA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-06%2Fde696720-a86e-11ea-ae67-9fe53df1bf3a&h=23ee66ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行政會議成員、新民黨主席葉劉淑儀表示，將來審理涉及「港區國安法」的案件，不適合安排陪審員審訊，因陪審員會有很多不同理由拒絕參與審訊。<br />\n<br />\n曾任保安局局長的葉劉淑儀，出席一個電台節目後，回應當年推動《基本法》23條立法時，後期於條例草案加入必須有陪審員審訊的建議，但現時認為不適合是否因擔心社會氣氛改變，不少人對立法反感，如設陪審團對案件不利。葉劉淑儀說，過去本港極少審理涉及國家安全的案件，加上陪審團可能會驚被「起底」，因此認為不適合。<br />\n<br />\n對於近期不少港人續領英國國民海外護照(BNO)，葉劉淑儀說，現時仍未有細節，如果只能旅遊不能工作，並無作用。除非英國大幅修改入境規例，列明不需符合技能、從事短缺工種等要求，甚至表明會接受35萬護照持有人，否則港人好難在當地生活，而且要留在英國6年才取得居英權，這段時間要交英國稅項，又無法享受當地福利。<br />\n<br />\n她又批評，英國如提供渠道，容許持英國國民海外護照的港人擁有居英權，實際上是違反《中英聯合聲明》的備忘錄。"},{"pid":"6bd507e90d986fff63eca2f10fc24bf448b288c0","tid":2054664,"uid":37596,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T10:36:43.000Z","msg":"其實訪問葉劉有咩用,9UP到完場?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5058d54d48ec782089c03876753df6f1543d70c5","tid":2054664,"uid":351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T10:36:53.000Z","msg":"對案件不利所以唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c30aaa90d625170b97e2ddf2d2359a79193475b","tid":2054664,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T10:38:24.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"d74fd3777d5ff3e3e3608cf0e25494d1ba9b51b7","tid":2054664,"uid":132810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T10:38:40.000Z","msg":"即係你地政府想點就點囉<br />\n<br />\n當啲市民冇生命"},{"pid":"8bedfcc0fa6bf2d4cd73b33331feff8f585bd926","tid":2054664,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T10:39:33.000Z","msg":"一陣上面出事又縮<br />\n呢班落重注保皇黨又變condom"},{"pid":"4965d7a9aee95ad95254c867dfbbec3d2fd2d6f6","tid":2054664,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T10:40:12.000Z","msg":"陪審團被起底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講緊審梁天琦案時有國安影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8521d2a92bc68fa68a312bb2557309b86426e121","tid":2054664,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T10:41:16.000Z","msg":"加速!!"},{"pid":"b599c43bab0fd6a56f2a3de46df04dd93cfd3c26","tid":2054664,"uid":279298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T10:42:36.000Z","msg":"根本同法國大革命前d獨裁皇帝冇分別<br />\n遲早一日我地要送曬佢地上斷頭枱斬首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0670af7929b0afca6cbc0c7454b224e2ecdb3012","tid":2054664,"uid":76135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T11:16:30.000Z","msg":"周星馳靶場式&ldquo;罪無可恕，無需審判，即時槍決&rdquo;. 你想點就點"}]}